<h3><a name="ref3">Implementation</a></h3>
<p>We enhanced BioThesaurus, developed by the lab, with gene/protein-related ontologies and categories and Onto-BioThesaurus is obtained by</p>
<ul>
	<li>Use ontology-alignment techniques to map names in BioThesaurus to gene/protein-related ontologies for recognizing systematic ambiguity of a name.</li>
	<li>Use corpus-based approaches to mine and ontology-enabled reasoning to enrich BioThesaurus and enable query expansion.</li>
</ul>
